{"tid":1000932,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人大個左就會慢慢學識自己一個","createTime":"2019-01-29T18:43:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T01:00:58.000Z","uid":66577,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e814831f10f8e442fe95d5ae47ff471a749a533c","tid":1000932,"uid":66577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T18:43:21.000Z","msg":"明明先得廿頭<br />\n但個個兄弟要番工要陪女 要諗升職諗搵錢<br />\n成班人已經唔似以前咁夜晚吹住水打機<br />\n<br />\n有空閒時間一係忙公司嘢<br />\n一係就已經攰到冇力水郁<br />\n唔會再約到出黎一齊跑步打牌食糖水<br />\n<br />\n然後大家嘅假期要獻俾自己重要嘅人<br />\n全男班嘅痴線旅行團慢慢會搞唔成<br />\n<br />\n真係好唔撚捨得你地<br />\n可惜我地已經慢慢長大<br />\n<br />\n或者身為毒撚嘅我會慢慢習慣變做孤零零一單友<br />\n然後享受呢個成長嘅過程<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97324ee8d4a039b45cd2dd71066ddec58d351948","tid":1000932,"uid":198637,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T19:02:13.000Z","msg":"其實孤獨並不可怕 應該要享受而非害怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbfc9db004c7cafa9c4cfa55f9c6440ada646abd","tid":1000932,"uid":66577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97324ee8d4a039b45cd2dd71066ddec58d351948","tid":1000932,"uid":198637,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T19:02:13.000Z","msg":"其實孤獨並不可怕 應該要享受而非害怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T19:08:09.000Z","msg":"係唔捨得佢地<br />\n<br />\n今日連最後一位廢青手足都踏入左現充階段<br />\n係時候自己都面對下自己嘅問題了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f1bbcc7a23625e18690df31fde5004b57a1b992","tid":1000932,"uid":232594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T19:14:02.000Z","msg":"慢慢就會可以捨得<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  應該<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f363cc757dc17fab5979291abfc6b247a9174dd5","tid":1000932,"uid":136625,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T19:21:28.000Z","msg":"奉勸未踏足社會嘅你哋仲有得同兄弟打